      <h2>Final Product Pain Points</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Fallbacks not good. No CSS works well, however no JS means it breaks the "Enter Here"</li>
        <li>Terrible accesibility -- which in hindsight is the dumbest thing here because this is for a hospital. We later found out that this was only for doctors but that really didn't make it much better.</li>
        <li>The sparkle animation on the key is definitely a machine overheater when it's active.</li>
        <li>The mobile experience is not that enjoyable, some things can be clicked accidentally.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Pushing the Project Further</h2>
      <p>I was actually hunting to the sparkles as more of a feature over the entire page but since it was terrible for perfomance I only let it show when the key was hovered. It's a shame too because it would have added so much more atmosphere.</p>

